vulkan:
vulkan: Vulkan is a new generation graphics and compute API that provides
vulkan: high-efficiency, cross-platform access to modern GPUs used in a wide
vulkan: variety of devices from PCs and consoles to mobile phones and embedded
vulkan: platforms.
vulkan: This package contains the reference ICD loader and validation layers
vulkan: for Vulkan.
